Sida caadiga ah, marka uu fayrasku galo qofka uu ku dhacay, waxaa marka hore lagu gartaa difaaca jirka ee soo-dhoweynta kala-soocidda (PRR) oo ay ku jiraan C-reg-like, TLR, NLR iyo RLR.
Si kala duwan, fayraska wuxuu keenaa qandho, bararka unugyada, iyo isku-darka borotiinka nooca I (IFN) ee loo yaqaan 'anti-viral resistance' oo yareeya faafitaanka fayraska oo dib u kiciya cudurka.
