Russell Zimmerman, oo ah madaxa fulinta ee Ururka Ganacsiga Australia, ayaa sheegay in ganacsatadu ay kordhin karaan saamiyada, laakiin xeerarka gawaarida xamuulka qaada ee ay soo saareen golaha deegaanka ayaa caqabad ku noqday.
Wuxuu aaminsan yahay in qiimaha badeecada uu kor u kici doono, iyadoo shirkadaha deynta ay isku dayaan inay daboolaan baahida macaamiisha, iyagoo siinaya xayeysiis yar.
