Cudurka hargabka ee doofaarka ee 2009 iyo COVID-19 ee 2020 ayaa wadamada u horseeday inay sii xoojiyaan fahamka muhiimada ay leedahay dhaqidda gacmaha saabuun iyo saabuun si looga hortago faafitaanka cudurrada faafa.
