Dhamaadkii bishii Febraayo 2020, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) wuxuu ku dhawaaqay in aysan jirin tallaal la filayo oo loogu talagalay SARS-CoV-2, oo ah cudurka keena, 18 bilood ka hor.
Shan tallaal ayaa weli ku jiray tijaabooyinka wajiga 1aad bishii Abriil.
COVID-19 waxaa la ogaaday bishii Diseembar 2019.
