Bishii Abriil, khubarada CEPI waxay ku dhawaaqeen in 10 nooc oo kala duwan oo tiknoolajiyad ah ay ku jiraan cilmi baarista iyo horumarinta horaanta 2020 si loo horumariyo tallaal awood leh oo ka hortaga COVID-19.
