Tallaabada labaad waa in la isticmaalo qaybaha tallaalka, taas oo ah habka loo sameeyo tallaal kaasoo ka dhigaya in nidaamka difaaca jirka uu ogaado jirka in uu jiro qaybo ka mid ah fayraska.
