Cilmi-baarista Shiinaha waxay diiradda saareysaa daaweynta caadiga ah ee cudurrada fayraska, iyadoo sagaal tijaabo oo wajiga III ah oo remdesivir ah ay ka socdaan dalal badan oo kala duwan iyadoo la filayo in warbixinta la soo saaro dhammaadka Abriil.
Laga soo bilaabo Abriil 2020, waxaa jira tijaabooyin tijaabo ah oo ku saabsan daawooyinka COVID-19. Daawooyin badan oo caadi ah oo loo isticmaalo in lagu daaweeyo cudurrada fayraska ah ayaa lagu baaray daaweynta COVID-19, oo ay ka mid yihiin remdesivir, chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir iyo lopinavir/ritonavir oo lagu daray interferon beta.
Ilaa Abriil 2020, waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in remdesivir uu yahay mid waxtar leh.
