Tijaabooyinka wajiga III ee Mareykanka, Kanada iyo Talyaaniga ayaa socda. Chloroquine, oo loo isticmaalo daaweynta kale ee cudurka duumada, ayaa la tijaabiyey bishii Febraayo 2020, iyadoo la helay natiijooyin hordhac ah.
